      <li><a class="trending-bar__link" href="https://editorial.rottentomatoes.com/article/pride-month-2026-movies-tv-streaming/"  data-qa="trending-bar-item"> Pride Month </a></li>
      
      <li><a class="trending-bar__link" href="https://editorial.rottentomatoes.com/article/app/"  data-qa="trending-bar-item"> Rotten Tomatoes App  </a></li>
      
